856
01:02:35.255 --> 01:02:36.756
Fucking aliens.

857
01:02:36.757 --> 01:02:45.014
♪

858
01:02:45.015 --> 01:02:46.265
[ Camera whirs ]

859
01:02:46.266 --> 01:02:50.937
