860
01:02:50.938 --> 01:02:54.482
Hull breach. Hull breach.

861
01:02:54.483 --> 01:02:56.651
Hull bre--
[ Beep. static hisses ]

862
01:02:56.652 --> 01:03:04.033
♪

863
01:03:04.034 --> 01:03:05.326
